short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Extension Provides Dark Mode for Jupyter before it is released officially

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tired of straining your eyes due to whites when everywhere you have dark mode on? Well, wait no further. Presenting Dark Mode for Jupyter Notebook. Especially helpful for programmers who spend hours staring at the notebook. Jupyter has never been this relaxing!
